Dyslexia
[[Image:Dyslexiashirt.jpg|thumb|400px| [[truth|Tru]].]]

'''liysDexia''' is a diesaes ersulitng in difcifutlys in raedign, wirtign and spenligl, sa wlel sa soemtiems infleuncign shrot-trem mermoy, mahtemitasc, concetnartoin, persalno hyegien and sqeuencign. The medacil trem for oen who sufefrs from dylsexai is "a big spaz".

[[Self-diagnosed|Ferqulenty cliamed as an excuse]] by ploepe on the [[internet|intrenet]] hwo:

* cantno splel becusea all thye raed aer [[Livejournal]] etrines by ohter [['tard|trads]] hwo slimiarly cantno splel, or becusea thye aer two [[Ritalin|Riltaiend]] too hit kyes in teh crorcet order; and/or
* dindt bothre to raed whevtaer sauce post thye aer repsondign too - noet that thiis is an unusaul usgae, becusea mots ploepe thnik dylsexai is awl abuot splelign.

[[IRL|RIL]] ilsdexiks otfan uz thire codnison az un [[Lie|exquz]] for been jurkz ur [[Butthurt|havn no sence ov humr]].

Dylsexci ploepe shluod not meak [http://www.iamdyslexic.com/ ''websiets''].

[[Truth|The onyl knwon crue for dylsexai is a lagre bwol of alhpaebt suop.]]
 
